'''月經紅'''（{{lang-en|''Period Red''}}）<ref>開心三口組，星島A1中文電台，2020-10-12.</ref>是[[Pantone|Pantone]]因應[[瑞典|瑞典]]女性用品品牌''[[Intimina|Intimina]]''的請求，為協助掃除對[[月經|月經]]的污名化，從而將這名字指定於一種紅色色調<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/30/business/pantone-color.html |title=Pantone’s Newest Color Is a Nod to Menstruation: Period Red |newspaper=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]] |date=2020-09-30 |access-date=2020-10-12 |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201201531/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/30/business/pantone-color.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="pantone">{{cite news |url=https://www.pantone.com/color-intelligence/articles/case-studies/the-creation-of-period |title=The Creation of Period: CREATING A RED HUE TO BREAK DOWN THE STIGMA SURROUNDING MENSTRUATION |publisher=[[Pantone|Pantone]] |access-date=2020-10-12 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103153052/https://www.pantone.com/color-intelligence/articles/case-studies/the-creation-of-period |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這種紅色色調較原來各個血紅色的定義更為明亮。在華語地區，亦有隨同對月經的避違而稱呼這種紅色為'''姨媽紅'''<ref name="jjwxc">{{cite book |chapter=第35章 |title=尖叫女王 |author=银发死鱼眼 |year=2018 |edition=2019年修訂 |publisher=晋江文學城 |date=2019-07-29 |access-date=2021-07-25 |language=zh-hans }}</ref>。

